item.title: Environmental Considerations
item.description: Keep the system dry and protect it from harmful ingress of water. The camera includes a rating of IPX1: protection against vertically falling drops of water. See Specifications for temperature and humidity considerations. WARNING To prevent fire or shock hazard, do not expose system to rain or moisture. This system is not suitable for use in the presence of flammable anesthetics mixture with air or with oxygen.
